oc.dateCreated)=:month  and year(doc.dateCreated)=:year '),(4,3,'Deze query geeft inzichten in het aantal documenten, gesorteerd per documenttype.','select doc from Document doc where doc.documentType.name=:value and month(doc.dateCreated)=:month and year(doc.dateCreated)=:year','Deze query geeft inzichten in het aantal documenten, gesorteerd per documenttype.','aantalDocumenten','select month(doc.dateCreated), doc.documentType, count(*) from Document doc where year(doc.dateCreated)=:year group by doc.documentType, month(doc.dateCreated)','Overzicht per documenttype','','select count(*) from Document doc where doc.documentType.name=:value and month(doc.dateCreated)=:month and year(doc.dateCreated)=:year');
